dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. In lower margin: Tome VIII in 4⁰. no. 5. Tome 4. in 8⁰. page 190. From: Histoire générale des voyages ... Paris : Didot, 1746-1789. cf. Parry, D.E. Cartography of the East Indian Islands, p. 193.
